  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 47-7-37.1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE STANDARD OF PROOF THAT A COURT USES WHEN DETERMINING WHETHER AN OFFENDERS PROBATION MAY BE REVOKED; TO PROVIDE THAT PROBATION, POST-RELEASE SUPERVISION OR SUSPENSION OF SENTENCE MAY BE REVOKED PRIOR TO ITS COMMENCEMENT IF A NEW FELONY CRIME IS COMMITTED PRIOR TO ITS COMMENCEMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
